add support for new tag:
code.<langauage_name> 
it will behavior like the code tag, except this time it can generate a codeblock for a specific language <langauage_name>
example:
<input>
code.php {
  echo "hello world";
}
</input>
<output>
```php
echo "hello world"
```
</output>
<input>
code.bash:npm run build
</input>
<output>
```bash
npm run build
```
</output>
